    "This capability also improves the model's proficiency in interpreting numerical data, enabling accurate evaluations of clinical indicators for normalcy.",
    "The Data Understanding dimension enhances the model's ability to process medical text, such as patient reports and long-form records like longitudinal follow-ups.",
    "Lastly, the Trustworthiness dimension focuses on minimizing hallucinations during medical task execution, thereby improving the model's reliability in clinical applications.",
    "There are two types of errors in the process of an agent utilizing tools to solve problems.",
    "The first is tool selection errors, as discussed in Section 5.5, where the agent employs an inappropriate tool for the task."
